sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor KH as Khach hang
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant AuthDB as Auth DB
    participant CS as Customer Service
    participant CustDB as Customer DB

    KH->>GW: POST /api/auth/register
    Note over KH,GW: username, password<br/>fullName, email, phoneNumber
    GW->>Auth: Forward request

    activate Auth

    Auth->>AuthDB: findByUsername(username)
    AuthDB-->>Auth: result

    alt Username da ton tai
        Auth-->>GW: 409 Conflict
        GW-->>KH: Ten dang nhap da ton tai
    else Username hop le
        Auth->>Auth: bcrypt.hash(password, salt=10)
        Auth->>AuthDB: account.create - userType=CUSTOMER
        AuthDB-->>Auth: account record

        Auth->>AuthDB: role.findByName - CUSTOMER
        AuthDB-->>Auth: role record
        Auth->>AuthDB: accountRole.assign(accountId, roleId)

        Auth->>CS: POST /internal/create-from-account
        Note over Auth,CS: accountId, username<br/>fullName, email, phoneNumber

        activate CS
        CS->>CustDB: customer.create<br/>customerType=REGULAR, points=0
        CustDB-->>CS: customer record
        CS-->>Auth: 201 Created
        deactivate CS

        Auth-->>GW: 201 Created
        Note over Auth,GW: accountId, username<br/>fullName, userType=CUSTOMER
        GW-->>KH: Dang ky thanh cong
    end

    deactivate Auth

